   TransTechnology
   Posts a Deficit,
   Suspends Payout
   ----
   By Rhonda L. Rundle
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/02/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
